---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Golf Cart Rentals - Masters Golf Cars" description="Reserve high-quality golf cart rentals for neighborhoods, events, and businesses across Central Florida.">
	<!-- Hero -->
	<section class="bg-white py-16">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">Golf Cart Rentals</h1>
			<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
				<div class="space-y-6">
					<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900">Enjoy the Convenience of Golf Cart Rentals</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-semibold">
						Renting a golf cart from us is the perfect solution if you need reliable, affordable, and convenient transportation of a golf cart without the commitment of ownership. Whether you need a temporary golf cart for a quick getaway or a large event, we make it easier for you. Other customers come to us after facing issues with golf carts from other dealerships. While we repair their golf carts, they take advantage of our golf cart rental options, staying mobile without interruption. Renting a golf cart from us will give you peace of mind, whether for a short-term fix or a specific need.
					</p>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-semibold">
						We have a minimum 3-day golf cart rental, with options for weekly or monthly rentals for individuals. We also offer golf cart fleet rentals for businesses hosting events across Central Florida.
					</p>
					<ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 font-semibold">
						<li>• Individual &amp; Event Rentals</li>
						<li>• Delivery &amp; Pick Up Options</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="w-full">
					<img
						src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/club-car_img_v68_250813_154125925.webp"
						alt="Club Car golf cart rental"
						class="w-full h-auto object-contain"
						loading="eager"
						width="800"
						height="600"
					/>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Rental Options -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-white">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 text-center mb-10">Our Golf Rental Options</h2>
			<p class="text-center text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10 font-semibold">
				Choose from 2, 4, or 6 passenger golf carts along with utility models to fit your itinerary. Every cart is cleaned, inspected, and fully charged before it heads out the door.
			</p>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-6 md:gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
				<div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl shadow-md p-8">
					<img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/2-seater-golf-cart_img_v63_250813_142814136.webp" alt="2-seater golf cart" class="mx-auto h-40 md:h-48 object-contain mb-4" loading="lazy" />
					<p class="font-semibold text-gray-800 text-lg">2-Seater Cart</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl shadow-md p-8">
					<img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/4-seater-golf-cart_img_v64_250813_142836603.webp" alt="4-seater golf cart" class="mx-auto h-40 md:h-48 object-contain mb-4" loading="lazy" />
					<p class="font-semibold text-gray-800 text-lg">4-Seater Cart</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl shadow-md p-8">
					<img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/6-seater-golf-cart_img_v65_250813_142855008.webp" alt="6-seater golf cart" class="mx-auto h-40 md:h-48 object-contain mb-4" loading="lazy" />
					<p class="font-semibold text-gray-800 text-lg">6-Seater Cart</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl shadow-md p-8">
					<img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/utility-cart_img_v66_250813_142912878.webp" alt="Utility golf cart" class="mx-auto h-40 md:h-48 object-contain mb-4" loading="lazy" />
					<p class="font-semibold text-gray-800 text-lg">Utility Cart</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Models Banner -->
	<section class="py-12" style="background-color: #86CA26;">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl border-2 border-gray-200 px-8 py-10 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6 md:gap-8">
				<div class="text-center lg:text-left mb-4 lg:mb-0">
					<h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 uppercase tracking-wide">Golf Cart Models for Rent</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-700 mt-2 font-semibold text-base md:text-lg">Premium brands ready for neighborhoods, events, and commercial sites.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-6 md:gap-8 w-full lg:w-auto">
					<img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/yamaha-logo-icon-0-0-250813163408273.webp" alt="Yamaha golf carts" class="h-12 md:h-16 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
					<img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/club-car-logo-icon-0-1-250813163408445.webp" alt="Club Car golf carts" class="h-12 md:h-16 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- How Rentals Work -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-white">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr,0.9fr] gap-12 items-center">
                <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-[36px] shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="aspect-[4/3]">
                        <img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/club-car_img_v68_250813_154125925.webp" alt="Club Car golf cart rental" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700">
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900">How Our Golf Cart Rentals Work</h3>
                    <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-3 leading-relaxed font-semibold">
                        <li>Complete the request form or call our rental specialists to get started.</li>
                        <li>Select the cart that fits your needs—choose seat count, accessories, and roof styles.</li>
                        <li>Reserve your rental with a minimal 3-day deposit (weekly &amp; monthly plans available).</li>
                        <li>Secure your reservation with a credit card.</li>
                        <li>We deliver to your location or you can pick up—and we'll handle return details when you're done.</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
	</section>

	<!-- Pricing & Terms -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr,0.9fr] gap-10 items-start">
				<div class="bg-white rounded-[32px] shadow-2xl border border-gray-200 p-8 md:p-10">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">Rental Pricing</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 font-semibold">
						Our pricing structure is flexible for your schedule and budget. Submit the rental form or call our team for exact availability and a custom quote.
					</p>
					<h4 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">Golf Cart Rental Terms &amp; Conditions</h4>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 font-semibold">
						<li><span class="font-black text-gray-900">Age Requirement:</span> Renters must be at least 21 years old.</li>
						<li><span class="font-black text-gray-900">Agreement:</span> A valid rental contract is required to reserve your cart.</li>
						<li><span class="font-black text-gray-900">Duration:</span> Minimum 3-day rentals; daily rentals available for certain events.</li>
						<li><span class="font-black text-gray-900">Delivery &amp; Pick-Up:</span> Offered within 50 miles; extended service areas available by request.</li>
						<li><span class="font-black text-gray-900">Service Area:</span> The Villages, Ocala, and surrounding Central Florida communities.</li>
					</ul>
					<div class="mt-8">
						<a href="/rentals" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 rounded-full bg-brand-green text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-wide hover:opacity-90 transition">Reserve Your Golf Cart Today</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-[36px] shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="aspect-[4/3]">
                        <img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/rent-a-golf-cart_img_v72_250813_161858549.webp" alt="Rent a golf cart" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
                    </div>
                </div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Why Rent -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-white">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr,0.85fr] gap-12 items-center">
				<div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
					<h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">Why Rent A Golf Cart From Us?</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4 font-semibold">
						Masters Golf Cars delivers top-quality rentals from brands you know and trust. We maintain our fleet to dealership standards, so you get a clean, reliable ride every time — complete with accessories tailored to your plans.
					</p>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 font-semibold">
						Our rental team handles everything from drop-off to pick-up, including charger setup, basic orientation, and on-call support during your rental window. We serve neighborhoods, resorts, weddings, festivals, corporate events, and commercial fleets across Central Florida.
					</p>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 font-semibold">
						<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
							<span class="text-brand-green text-xl leading-none font-black">•</span>
							<span>Flexible rental terms — daily, weekly, and monthly plans available.</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
							<span class="text-brand-green text-xl leading-none font-black">•</span>
							<span>Fully serviced carts with options for windshields, enclosures, coolers, and lighting upgrades.</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
							<span class="text-brand-green text-xl leading-none font-black">•</span>
							<span>Friendly customer support &amp; experienced delivery team.</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-[36px] shadow-2xl overflow-hidden w-full">
					<div class="aspect-[4/3]">
						<img src="/images/golf-cart-rentals-page/yamaha-quietech-efi_img_v71_250813_161157847.webp" alt="Golf cart rental delivery" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Reviews -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">Golf Cart Rental Reviews</h3>
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8 border border-gray-100">
					<div class="mb-4 flex gap-1 text-brand-green">
						{Array.from({ length: 5 }).map((_star, index) => (
							<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
							</svg>
						))}
					</div>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 font-semibold">
						"Fantastic people to work with. Delivered my rental cart on time as promised. Highly recommend!"
					</p>
					<p class="font-black text-gray-900">Scott Lennox</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8 border border-gray-100">
					<div class="mb-4 flex gap-1 text-brand-green">
						{Array.from({ length: 5 }).map((_star, index) => (
							<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
							</svg>
						))}
					</div>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 font-semibold">
						"They were awesome to work with! They gave us an excellent deal on a rental while they fixed ours. The staff is extremely knowledgeable and professional."
					</p>
					<p class="font-black text-gray-900">Megan O'Brien</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8 border border-gray-100">
					<div class="mb-4 flex gap-1 text-brand-green">
						{Array.from({ length: 5 }).map((_star, index) => (
							<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
							</svg>
						))}
					</div>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 font-semibold">
						"The carts were delivered the day before, so we weren't waiting on the day of. They performed the job and more. I would highly recommend renting carts from this great company with awesome staff."
					</p>
					<p class="font-black text-gray-900">Danielle Clark</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- FAQ -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-white">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 text-center mb-10">Golf Cart Rentals FAQs</h3>
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-3">
				<details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl px-5 py-4 shadow">
					<summary class="font-black text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">What is the minimum age to rent a golf cart?</summary>
					<p class="mt-3 text-gray-700 font-semibold">Renters must be at least 21 years old with a valid driver's license and insurance.</p>
				</details>
				<details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl px-5 py-4 shadow">
					<summary class="font-black text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">Can I rent a golf cart for an event?</summary>
					<p class="mt-3 text-gray-700 font-semibold">Absolutely. We support weddings, corporate gatherings, concerts, festivals, and multi-day sporting events with fleet rentals.</p>
				</details>
				<details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl px-5 py-4 shadow">
					<summary class="font-black text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">Do I need to pay a deposit?</summary>
					<p class="mt-3 text-gray-700 font-semibold">Yes. A refundable deposit is required to secure your reservation and will be credited toward your rental balance.</p>
				</details>
				<details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl px-5 py-4 shadow">
					<summary class="font-black text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">Can I extend my rental period?</summary>
					<p class="mt-3 text-gray-700 font-semibold">Most rentals can be extended with advance notice. Contact our team as soon as you know you'll need additional time.</p>
				</details>
				<details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl px-5 py-4 shadow">
					<summary class="font-black text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">Do you offer delivery for golf cart rentals?</summary>
					<p class="mt-3 text-gray-700 font-semibold">Yes, we deliver throughout Central Florida and offer convenient pickup options when you're finished.</p>
				</details>
			</div>
			<div class="text-center mt-12">
				<a href="/rentals" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-4 rounded-full bg-brand-green text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-wide hover:opacity-90 transition">
					Rent Your Golf Cart Today
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

